      <arrangement id="aspace_2cf09c59450b67335b820c7bd07417ce">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The collection is arranged by type of material.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_2c4ea4351e3df14886ddf8bf00d15f65">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of copies of select Annan papers from the United Nations, including interviews, correspondence, briefings, reports and speeches from Annan's tenure as United Nations Secretary-General from 1997 to 2007.   The majority of the papers in this collection are published and indexed in the <title render="italic">
               <part>Collected Papers of Kofi Annan, UN Secretary-General, 1997-2006</part>
            </title>, edited by Jean E. Krasno.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <originalsloc id="aspace_9416467974814a32ea0a8d86d9b368f7">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>Originals are in the United Nations, Archives and Records Management Section.</p>  
      </originalsloc>
